## Colour

One palette, paper-forward, one accent.

- Background: `bg-paper` (`#FAF8F5`) — the default canvas.
- Text: `text-ink` (`#3D3126`) — rich, warm dark.
- Accent: `text-accent` / `bg-accent` (`#B38B5D`) — used sparingly for one focal point per section (a CTA, a stat, a rule line).
- Never introduce raw hex values in components. All values live in `@theme` inside `globals.css`.
- Colour carries hierarchy: if you reach for a new colour to solve a layout problem, solve the layout problem instead.
- Dark sections (e.g. `bg-espresso-900` hero) are valid for contrast rhythm but limit to one or two per page.

---

## Structure

- **Section rhythm**: each section has one clear job. No section should attempt to do two things.
- **Hairline rules**: use `border-t border-ink/10` (or `border-paper/10` on dark) to separate content regions within a section — avoid heavy dividers.
- **Numbered / labeled sections**: editorial style uses explicit section labels (e.g. `01 Services`, `02 Pricing`) as eyebrows to orient the reader.
- **Asymmetry**: favour offset grids (`lg:grid-cols-[1.05fr_1fr]`) and intentional imbalance over symmetric two-column splits.
- **Whitespace**: padding/margin should feel generous at every breakpoint. When in doubt, add more vertical space, not less.
- Section order is fixed: `Header → Hero → Services → Pricing → About → QuoteSection → Contact → Footer`. Do not reorder without explicit instruction.

---

## Motion
- Scroll-reveal is handled by `useReveal` (`src/lib/use-reveal.ts`) + `.reveal` / `.is-visible` classes in `globals.css`. Use this pattern — do not add new animation libraries.
- `prefers-reduced-motion` is already respected globally in `globals.css`. Never add `transition` or `animation` without this coverage.

---

## Stack guardrails
- **Tokens first**: all design tokens (colours, fonts, shadows) live in `@theme` in `globals.css`. Use Tailwind utility classes that map to these tokens.
- **Content**: all copy, contact details, service names, and pricing live in `src/lib/site-config.ts`. Never hardcode them in components.
- **Accessibility**: `focus-visible` ring is set globally. Maintain colour contrast ratios (WCAG AA minimum).
